## Anti-Patterns to Avoid
- Using rem units instead of px
- Style-based class names instead of semantic names
- Multiple classes per element instead of comprehensive single classes
- Unsorted CSS properties
- Missing `!important` for library overrides
- Double underscores in BEM naming
